title: How Mike Mizanin Created ‘The Miz’ | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
'Challenge' legend and WWE superstar Mike ‘The Miz’ Mizanin joins Johnny this week to discuss how he turned his ‘Real World’ season and time on ‘The Challenge’ into the amazing career he has now, including but certainly not limited to multiple movies and his own reality series ‘Miz & Mrs.,’ which returns to your screens June 6.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Mike ‘The Miz’ Mizanin
Producer: Sasha Ashall
